{"text_id":40023,"tokens":["Understand"," that"," the"," Quran"," does"," not"," necessarily"," condemn"," homosexuality","."," While"," there"," are"," verses"," that"," describe"," homosexual"," behavior",","," many"," scholars"," argue"," that"," these"," verses"," are"," open"," to"," interpretation"," and"," should"," not"," be"," taken"," as"," a"," direct"," condemnation"," of"," homosexuality",".","\n\n","Know"," that"," gender"," identity"," is"," not"," addressed"," in"," the"," Quran","."," The"," Quran"," does"," not"," specifically"," mention"," or"," discuss"," transgender"," or"," non","-","binary"," identities","."," Therefore",","," any"," beliefs"," or"," opinions"," held"," about"," these"," identities"," are"," not"," based"," on"," religious"," text",".","\n\n","Look"," for"," the"," authenticity"," of"," a"," ha","dith"," before"," believing"," it","."," The"," ha","dith",","," which"," are"," sayings"," and"," actions"," attributed"," to"," the"," Prophet"," Muhammad",","," are"," not"," always"," reliable"," sources"," of"," information","."," It"," is"," important"," to"," verify"," the"," authenticity"," of"," a"," ha","dith"," before"," accepting"," it"," as"," fact",".","\n\n","Pray"," for"," Allah","'","s"," forgiveness",","," if"," you"," find"," it"," necessary","."," If"," you"," believe"," that"," you"," have"," done"," something"," wrong",","," it"," is"," always"," okay"," to"," pray"," for"," forgiveness","."," However",","," do"," not"," let"," guilt"," or"," shame"," consume"," you","."," Remember"," that"," Allah"," is"," the"," most"," merciful"," and"," the"," most"," forgiving",".","\n\n","Search"," for"," a"," safe"," place"," to"," express"," your"," faith","."," It"," is"," important"," to"," find"," a"," community"," where"," you"," can"," practice"," and"," express"," your"," faith"," without"," fear"," of"," judgment"," or"," discrimination","."," Consider"," reaching"," out"," to"," LGBT","-","friendly"," mosques"," or"," online"," communities",".","\n\n","Recognize"," that"," religion"," evolves"," to"," fit"," the"," time"," period","."," Religious"," beliefs"," and"," practices"," may"," change"," and"," adapt"," over"," time"," to"," reflect"," the"," values"," and"," norms"," of"," a"," particular"," culture"," or"," society","."," This"," does"," not"," mean"," that"," the"," core"," beliefs"," of"," Islam"," are"," any"," less"," valid"," or"," true",".","\n\n","Remember"," that"," only"," Allah"," can"," truly"," judge"," what"," is"," right"," or"," wrong","."," Ultimately",","," it"," is"," up"," to"," Allah"," to"," judge"," our"," actions"," and"," intentions","."," Trust"," in"," Allah","'","s"," wisdom"," and"," mercy",".","\n\n","Avoid"," resc","inding"," your"," faith"," just"," because"," you","'","re"," LGBT","+."," Being"," LGBT","+"," is"," not"," a"," sin",","," and"," it"," does"," not"," make"," you"," any"," less"," of"," a"," Muslim","."," Do"," not"," let"," anyone",","," including"," yourself",","," convince"," you"," otherwise",".","\n\n","Seek"," acceptance"," from"," yourself"," first",","," rather"," than"," others","."," It"," is"," important"," to"," love"," and"," accept"," yourself"," for"," who"," you"," are"," before"," seeking"," acceptance"," from"," others","."," This"," will"," ultimately"," lead"," to"," greater"," happiness"," and"," fulfillment",".","\n\n","Acknowledge"," how"," you"," feel","."," Whether"," you"," are"," attracted"," to"," the"," same"," gender",","," feel"," uncomfortable"," in"," your"," assigned"," gender",","," or"," both",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," acknowledge"," and"," accept"," these"," feelings",".","\n\n","Research"," your"," identity","."," Educate"," yourself"],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}